						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="d-none bfcm-waitlist__thank-you text-center px-0 py-2">
						<a href="#" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary btn-block">Shop Coco & Eve</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="col-12 font-size-xs text-lg-center py-2 p-lg-0 my-0 mt-lg-5">
					*Customers who sign up to our waitlist through SMS or email address will be given 24 hours early access to our Black Friday sale, and a chance to be one of three to win $500 usd worth of products. Black Friday early access, and contest winners will be notified via email. Black Friday early access will run from November 24, 2020 12:00am PST to November 24, 2020 11:50pm PST. Black Friday offer cannot be used in conjunction with any other code, offer or promotion. Coco & Eve reserves the right to cancel or alter any promotion without prior notice. In the event of any dispute, the decision of Coco & Eve is final.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	{{> sections/footer}}

	{{> js jquery=true bootstrap=true main=true }}
</body>
</html>
